A cloaking device has been used in many different science fiction shows. In these sci-fi(science fiction) shows, it is usually not the protaganist who uses the device, but rather an unseen enemy. The idea for the cloaking device was inveneted by Star Trek Creator, Gene Roddenberry. Roddenberry also created Earth:Final Conflict, Andromeda, and Star Trek: The Next Generation. Gene Roddeneberry Died in 1996.